'''2-硝基乙醇'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为NO<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>OH。它可由[[硝基甲烷|硝基甲烷]]和[[甲醛|甲醛]]在碱性条件下反应制得。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=137|issue=1|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=2015-01-14|pages=130–133|doi=10.1021/ja5117556|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ja5117556|title=Organocatalytic Enantioselective Formal C(sp 2 )–H Alkylation|accessdate=2020-06-28|author=Madhu Sudan Manna, Santanu Mukherjee}}</ref>其它制备方法还有[[2-碘乙醇|2-碘乙醇]]和[[亚硝酸银|亚硝酸银]]的反应<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=76|issue=12|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=1954-06|pages=3227–3228|doi=10.1021/ja01641a044|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01641a044|title=The Nitroethylation of Indole. A New Synthesis of Tryptamine|accessdate=2020-06-28|author=Wayland E. Noland, Philip J. Hartman}}</ref>及[[环氧乙烷|环氧乙烷]]和[[亚硝酸钠|亚硝酸钠]]的反应<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Synthetic Communications|volume=35|issue=6|language=en|issn=0039-7911|date=2005-03|pages=873–878|doi=10.1081/SCC-200051043|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1081/SCC-200051043|title=LaCl 3 · 7H 2 O‐Promoted Regioselective Ring Opening of Epoxides Using NaNO 2 in Ether–Water System: A Facile Synthesis of 2‐Nitroalcohols|accessdate=2020-06-28|author=Jagat C. Borah, Siddhartha Gogoi, Joshodeep Boruwa, Nabin C. Barua}}</ref>。它和[[乙酰氯|乙酰氯]]反应，可以得到乙酸-2-硝基乙酯。<ref>Colin Philip Leslie. The stereochemistry of the SE2 reaction of pentadienylsilanes [Dissertation], 1994.  Department of Chemistry, University of Cambridge. 1630067.</ref>

